This paper presents a retrieval approach for visual media collections that allows users to query by sketching concept maps, merging sketch-based retrieval with the search for semantic labels. This involves taking into account the semantic concepts themselves, their semantic relations, and their spatial context. As such, this paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV), Information Retrieval (cs.IR), Multimedia (cs.MM), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), and Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-categories of arXiv CS.
